message.body: Hey mang. Another question for ya: Did you borrow a lil 1-2 person tent from us for some trip a few years ago?? PS-where the shit you been at??
Yoooo. Yea, at farm party like forevs ago. I'm almost certain I gave it back to you.
For where am at, been in philly, I quit urban, got a job working from home for a company in virginia
So, I'll be around in philly

Word. I figured it might have popped up during your recent move. I personally never saw it again. I'm not gonna make a big deal out of it tho. It's not like I use it all the time. You live out near the Riverview/target or whatevs with steph now right? We should all do something soon.
